<div class="center hero-unit" bgcolor="black">

<div align="center">
  <div class="well well-sm" style="width: 390px" color="black">
  	<%= image_tag("background.png") %>
    <h5 color = 'white'>Destroy the X Robots by making them crash into each other or crash into a pile of radioactive debris</h5>
    <%= link_to "Download for Windows", pc_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>

    <h3>Movement</h3>
    <div align="left">
    <h5>The "O" character has letters around it indicating
    <br>which direction you can move.
    <br>After you move one space,
    <br>every X Robot will move towards you.
    <br>Watch them DIE when they touch the radioactive debris (the red # characters)
    </h5></div>
    
    <h3>Teleportation</h3>
    <div align="left">
    <h5>Type a 'T' and you will be placed someplace new.
    <br>That might kill you.
    </h5></div>
    
    <h3>The Ultimate Screwdriver</h3>
    <div align="left">
    <h5>If an X Robot is next to you, the screwdriver
    	<br>will short their power source and they die.
    <br>The screw driver will turn up to 8 X robots into rubble
    <br>if you are sorrounded
    <br>The screwdriver works only once per screen, 
    <br>choose wisely!
    </h5></div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>